      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit refresh and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with refreshed control arm bushings for precise turn-in. This example represents a mechanically sorted driver's car, exhibiting strong compression across all cylinders and a crisp, notch-free shifter feel.",
